  "description": "A useful PocketMine-MP plugin that allows you to create crates in-game!",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-complexcrates\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#complexcrates\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ComplexCrates</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/ComplexCrates\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a899554d4c8d20cbe32bdc3d7bf0756701ee4be22ac2013e42c95dc234ed91e5/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e73746174652f436f6d706c6578437261746573\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.state/ComplexCrates\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/ComplexCrates\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a7eaaac55cbda7ef04511e8ed7825dcad6832509202d320b285e07013b733742/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e6170692f436f6d706c6578437261746573\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.api/ComplexCrates\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/ComplexCrates\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/eb63720d54b3e782b8f38077651bf26705acbdd14e1fbf844ff30a2813b11fde/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e646c2e746f74616c2f436f6d706c6578437261746573\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl.total/ComplexCrates\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/ComplexCrates\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1b6646cbcfc0fd5c82db6501dcfa0ae85921c689a0fded14e81ea15faa7a0ae0/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e646c2f436f6d706c6578437261746573\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl/ComplexCrates\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>A useful PocketMine-MP plugin that allows you to create crates in-game!</p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-commands\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#commands\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Commands</h1>\n<p>Main command: <code>/crate</code>\nSub commands:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<code>create</code> - Creates a crate</li>\n<li>\n<code>edit</code> - Edits a crate</li>\n<li>\n<code>remove</code> - Removes a crate</li>\n<li>\n<code>list</code> - Lists all crates</li>\n<li>\n<code>givekey</code> - Gives key to player</li>\n<li>\n<code>givekey-all</code> - Gives key to all players</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-todo\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#todo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>TODO</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>adding more languages</li>\n<li>there can be some bugfixes but i dont think so</li>\n<li>custom language file ? maybe?</li>\n<li>API? maaybe if they want</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-reporting-bugs\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#reporting-bugs\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Reporting bugs</h1>\n<p><strong>You may open an issue on the ComplexCrates GitHub repository for report bugs</strong>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexCrates/issues\">https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexCrates/issues</a></p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
